data.description: Maintenance-Free Living and even a gorgeous pool you will never have to clean!  Don’t hire anyone to roof this home, don’t pay a lawn service, and forget about having “waste management” fees on your utility bill. It is all covered for you! This beautifully renovated single story, 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom end unit in the highly sought-after Pebble Creek Villas can be yours in a location that can’t be beat! You won’t even need a car to get to Publix, Fresh Market, Uppercrust, Bagel Bakery, dry cleaners, restaurants, banks, credit unions and more-this is an incredibly convenient location! Just upon entering, you will see no stairs at all as you notice the soaring vaulted ceilings in the dining and living areas with lots of natural light. The kitchen has undergone a stunning transformation, new soft close, solid wood cabinets, new fixtures, featuring upgraded granite tile countertops, a gorgeous backsplash and new stainless steel appliances. The home features luxury vinyl plank in the community areas AND the bedrooms! No carpet, the bathroom has tile! The primary bath has been updated with new vanity, sink, toilet and flooring with a new toilet in second bath as well. The inviting patio is a great place to grab your morning coffee while you enjoy your view of nature view (no neighbors right behind you!). And it is not just a screened-in patio, it has windows that can be closed if you want to make it a 4 seasons room. The wood burning fireplace for the cool fall and winter evenings will make things comfy and cozy for you when the temperature dips outside! The pool and the clubhouse are wonderful amenities. This is an opportunity you don't want to miss! Contact us today to schedule your tour.
